claim.claim-text:
A method for producing:
(a) rebaudioside M, comprising providing a rebaudioside D, NDP, sucrose, a sucrose synthase of any one of claims 1-5, and at least one engineered glycosyltransferase, combining said rebaudioside D substrate, NDP, sucrose, sucrose synthase, and glycosyltransferase under conditions such that rebaudioside M is produced;
(b) producing rebaudioside A and/or rebaudioside I comprising providing a stevioside substrate, NDP, sucrose, a sucrose synthase of any one of claims 1-5, and at least one engineered glycosyltransferase , combining said stevioside substrate, NDP, sucrose, sucrose synthase, and glycosyltransferase under conditions such that rebaudioside A and/or rebaudioside I is produced;
(c) rebaudioside D, comprising providing a stevioside substrate, NDP, sucrose, a sucrose synthase of any one of claims 1-5, and at least one engineered glycosyltransferase , combining said stevioside substrate, NDP, sucrose, sucrose synthase, and glycosyltransferase under conditions such that rebaudioside D is produced;
(d) rebaudioside M, comprising providing a stevioside substrate comprising at least one stevioside and/or a mixture of steviosides and rebA, NDP, sucrose, a sucrose synthase of any one of claims 1-5, and at least one engineered glycosyltransferase , combining said stevioside substrate, NDP, sucrose, sucrose synthase, and glycosyltransferase under conditions such that rebaudioside M is produced; or
(e) rebaudioside M, comprising providing a stevioside substrate, NDP, sucrose, at least one sucrose synthase of claims 1-5, and at least one engineered glycosyltransferase, combining said stevioside substrate, NDP, and glycosyltransferase under conditions such that rebaudioside A is first produced, rebaudioside D and/or rebaudioside I is then produced, and rebaudioside M finally produced.
